requirements.txt
Python dependencies that are not within the Python Standard library
Must be written in this file
Enable the program to install any modules / packages needed before running the code

pyproject.toml
needed to declare the files in your python package and all the metadata for it that will show in PyPi. 
A tool like flit can process the pyproject. toml file into a package that can be uploaded to PyPi or installed with pip.
